                     <rs type="person" ref="pe__johann_von_tierna_QGW_II_I_1018"><roleName type="title">hern</roleName> Jansen von Tirna, <roleName type="occ" corresp="org__wien">purgermaister</roleName> und <roleName type="occ" corresp="org__wien">munsmaister</roleName>, und <roleName type="occ" corresp="org__wien">des rates gemain der stat ze
